OL,3,CMan charged with drug offences runs
OL,4,Cout of court
OL,6,FA man charged with a series of drug
OL,7,Foffences has run out of court.
OL,9,FCCTV caught Abu Faye, 26, from Hackney
OL,10,Ffleeing Croydon Crown Court on foot.
OL,12,FPolice are trying to find him and are
OL,13,Fasking the public to get in touch if
OL,14,Fthey spot him.
OL,16,FFaye has been charged with five counts
OL,17,Fof possession with intent to supply
OL,18,Fand five counts of possession of Class
OL,19,FA and Class B drugs.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/3
