OL,3,CMan charged with drug offences runs
OL,4,Cout of court
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to the latter five
OL,7,Fcharges, prompting the judge to seek
OL,8,Fremand.
OL,10,FOfficers say he has links to Penge and
OL,11,FCambridge.
OL,13,FFaye should not be approached, but
OL,14,Fmembers of the public should call 999
OL,15,Fquoting CAD 4966/17MARCH if they see
OL,16,Fhim.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/3
