OL,3,CMan charged with drug offences runs
OL,4,Cout of court
OL,6,FIn a statement the Met said: "On
OL,7,FTuesday, 17 March at 16:03hrs, the Met
OL,8,Fwas informed by the prison service
OL,9,Fthat Abu Faye, 26, from Hackney, had
OL,10,Fleft Croydon Crown Court during a
OL,11,Fhearing for drug-related offences."
